/target
**/target

# Python bytecode cache from inventory helper scripts
**/__pycache__/

# Generated by vantage-ui when it scaffolds/opens an inventory:
# Per-model redb caches — regenerated at runtime by vantage-ui. Ignore
# everywhere, not just under inventory/, so no app can leak them into git.
**/.cache/
**/inventory/**/*-schema-*.json
# Installed agent-skill bundles (reproducible — installed under .agents/skills,
# treated like vendored deps; AGENTS.md describing them is committed).
**/.agents/

# Per-app local secrets — inventory/.env can hold real credentials (AWS keys,
# tokens). Never commit; .env.example documents the shape.
**/inventory/.env
# Per-folder READMEs the scaffolder writes into datasource/table/page/menu/action
**/inventory/datasource/README.md
**/inventory/table/README.md
**/inventory/page/README.md
**/inventory/menu/README.md
**/inventory/action/README.md

# Downloaded app binary / DMG (CI fetches these at runtime)
/vantage.dmg
/Vantage*.app
latest.json

.DS_Store
